<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Jan1933"><font color="red">10 January 1933</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): I have been to see Mr Morley of Faber and Faber and he is quite willing to bring out a limited edition of the new fragment from Work in Progress but before making any suggestion with regard to terms, etc, he wishes to wait and hear whether the Viking Press are willing to collaborate in such an edition. </div>
